Title: Nisei (1)
Plot: An investigation into a video of an alien autopsy puts Mulder and Scully in the middle of a conspiracy involving WWII Japanese scientists brought to America to continue their experiments which may shed light on Scully's abduction.
Writer: Chris Carter, Howard Gordon, Frank Spotnitz
GuestStars: Stephen McHattie, Raymond J. Barry, Robert Ito, Gillian Barber, Corrine Koslo, Paul McLean, Yasuo Sakurai, Lori Ann Triolo, Roger Allford, Carrie Cain Sparks, Bob Wilde, Warren Takeuchi
